column16: Joe Mantiply intentionally walks Francisco Lindor.
Jason Kipnis hits a ground-rule double (34) on a fly ball to right-center field.   Roberto Perez scores.    Carlos Santana to 3rd.
Carlos Santana singles on a ground ball to right fielder J.  D.   Martinez.   Roberto Perez to 2nd.
Roberto Perez singles on a ground ball to left fielder Justin Upton.   Rajai Davis scores.
Juan Centeno out on a sacrifice bunt, pitcher Joe Mantiply to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.   Eddie Rosario to 2nd.
Eddie Rosario singles on a ground ball to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.
John Ryan Murphy grounds into a double play, shortstop Jose Iglesias to second baseman Ian Kinsler to first baseman Miguel Cabrera.   Kurt Suzuki out at 2nd.
Eduardo Escobar lines out to left fielder Tyler Collins.
Kurt Suzuki singles on a sharp line drive to center fielder Cameron Maybin.
Kennys Vargas homers (7) on a fly ball to left field.
Nolan Reimold grounds out, shortstop Dixon Machado to first baseman John Hicks.
Ryan Flaherty singles on a ground ball to center fielder JaCoby Jones.
Matt Wieters called out on strikes.
Jarrod Dyson flies out to center fielder Tyler Collins.
